item.comment: Great fun and easy to learn. Been playing it with my group for over a year and it is always different and funny. Lots of interaction, turnarounds and trying to prevent others doing what they want. Good for beginners and those who take things easily and enjoy a laugh. And there are nice combos and interesting "factoids" about each European country. A gem :)
